    "Table 5 below summarizes current studies on enhancing DL in plant disease diagnosis.",
    "An image dataset consists of digitized pictures that have been carefully selected for use in training, testing, and assessing the performance of computer vision algorithms.",
    "The data sets used to analyze leaves are built from primary data gathered in the fields.",
    "Because the statistics are based on visible characteristics of the leaves, they have a high degree of trustworthiness.",
    "Additionally, the data sets are separated into easily understandable portions."
